OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FDebbie Adlam tells ITV News
OL,8,FCorrespondent John Ray, the impact her
OL,9,Fson's death has had on the family and
OL,10,Fhow she feels about the prospect of PC
OL,11,FHarper's killers being back on the
OL,12,Fstreets
OL,14,FThe mother of police officer Andrew
OL,15,FHarper has told ITV News how
OL,16,F'devasted' and 'let down' her son
OL,17,Fwould be at the prospect of his
OL,18,Fkillers being released from prison
OL,19,Fearly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FDebbie Adlam spoke following reports
OL,8,Fthis week that the men responsible for
OL,9,FPC Harper's death, Jessie Cole and
OL,10,FAlbert Bowers, may have been eligible
OL,11,Ffor early release under a scheme
OL,12,Faiming to free up space in prisons.
OL,14,FAsked about Prime Minister Andy
OL,15,FBurnham's decision in his first week
OL,16,Fof government to pause the early
OL,17,Frelease scheme, Adlam said it was "a
OL,18,Fgood start" but is "not enough".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
