PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FPC Harper was 28 years old when he
OL,8,Fsustained fatal injuries while
OL,9,Fresponding to a quad bike theft in
OL,10,FSulhamstead, Berkshire, in August 2019.
OL,12,FHe died after getting caught in a
OL,13,Fstrap attached to the back of a car
OL,14,Fand dragged down a country road as
OL,15,Fthree teenage suspects fled the scene
OL,16,Fof the burglary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FJessie Cole and Albert Bowers, who
OL,8,Fwere passengers in the car and both 17
OL,9,Fyears old at the time, were handed 13
OL,10,Fyears in custody for manslaughter
OL,11,Fafter a trial at the Old Bailey in
OL,12,F2020.
OL,14,FEarlier this week the Ministry of
OL,15,FJustice (MoJ) confirmed that both men
OL,16,Fmight be eligible to be released from
OL,17,Fprison halfway through their sentences
OL,18,F` igniting a national outcry and
OL,19,Fprompting the government to step-in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FAsked how the events of this week have
OL,8,Fimpacted her, Adlam told ITV News:
OL,9,F"It's a different kind of thing that
OL,10,FI'm dealing with. We've been so much,
OL,11,Fthe pain is always there, so it's not
OL,12,Flike it's new pain specifically.
OL,14,F"We've got to keep going. Where we
OL,15,Fthought our task was done, it seems
OL,16,Fthat we've still got further to go.
OL,17,FAnd everything's done in Andrew's name
OL,18,Fand everything's done for justice for
OL,19,Fhim."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FAsked how she feels about the
OL,8,Fprospects of Cole and Bowers walking
OL,9,Fthe streets again, which despite
OL,10,FBurnham's pause is still a
OL,11,Fpossibility, Adlam said: "I'd be
OL,12,Fdevastated.
OL,14,F"Because I know from watching them
OL,15,Fwhen they were sentenced, and before
OL,16,Fthat, watching them in court every
OL,17,Fday... I saw their behaviour and their
OL,18,Fattitude."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FIn footage showing the pair being told
OL,8,Fthat they had killed PC Harper, Adlam
OL,9,Fsays "there was no shock or horror or
OL,10,Fany sign of anything", adding that she
OL,11,Fexpected to see "celebrations" from
OL,12,Fthe two killers upon their release.
OL,14,FAs for her son, Adlam says that PC
OL,15,FHarper would be "furious" at the
OL,16,Fprospect of his killers, or other
OL,17,Fserious offenders being back on the
OL,18,Fstreet before serving their full time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,F"It's a difficult question because I
OL,8,Fknow ultimately, he would be furious
OL,9,Fand so let down and just devastated by
OL,10,Fit all," she said.
OL,12,F"But how would he come across? That's
OL,13,Fa difficult one because he's always
OL,14,Fsuch a positive person that always had
OL,15,Fthat air about him of working his way
OL,16,Fthrough things."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,F"When you go to work and you're a
OL,8,Fpublic service, you're there to
OL,9,Fassist," Adlam added. "Nobody goes
OL,10,Fthere to do any harm to anybody - That
OL,11,Fis your calling mostly.
OL,13,F"I spoke to a lady the other day and I
OL,14,Fsaid to her, why would you choose to
OL,15,Fdo this now? And she said, if you cut
OL,16,Fme open, I'd be like a stick of rock.
OL,17,FIt runs right through me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,F"And I thought that actually explains
OL,8,Fvery well. That was how Andrew felt. I
OL,9,Fthink Andrew really was so perfect for
OL,10,Fthe policing role and I think we need
OL,11,Fto protect them.
OL,13,F"You know, things ultimately will
OL,14,Fhappen. You can never stop things
OL,15,Fhappening, but you can protect what
OL,16,Fhappens next."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,FOn the Burnham government's latest
OL,8,Fintervention, Adlam said: "It's not
OL,9,Fenough. It's a good start, and it
OL,10,Freally is a good basis to begin
OL,11,Fworking on some sensible alternatives
OL,12,Fand looking at options.
OL,14,F"For going forward, because there's so
OL,15,Fmany people this affects, it's not
OL,16,Fjust us. It's incredibly personal to
OL,17,Fus, but it's not just us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,F"And I think it really needs a good
OL,8,Flooking at, not just a quick, you
OL,9,Fknow, meeting and that's it. We'll
OL,10,Fmove on. It needs to be looked at
OL,11,Fthoroughly and that's what I'm hoping
OL,12,Ffor. You know, we want to see some
OL,13,Fresults from it.
OL,15,FAsked what she would tell the prime
OL,16,Fminister if she had the opportunity,
OL,17,FAdlam struggled to put her feelings
OL,18,Finto words.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784839668
OL,3,CPC Andrew Harper's mother says he'd be
OL,4,C'furious' if killers were released
OL,5,Cearly
OL,7,F"I think it's trying to bring home to
OL,8,Fhim how it actually feels to be in
OL,9,Fthis position," she said. "You can't
OL,10,Fput a lot of this into words.
OL,12,F"It's very much feelings that aren't
OL,13,Fexplainable, but the depth of knowing
OL,14,Fthat you've got to stand up and fight
OL,15,Fwith your every bone to make sure that
OL,16,Fyou've done everything you can really
OL,17,Faffects how you go forward as a
OL,18,Fperson."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
